| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5022 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0796e20f-3f47-509d-bfef-0159ecff4f72"
